 \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"its rules\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More to the point, high testosterone levels and the presence of XY or XXY chromosomes do not make a person male, or biologically a man.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"score\": 0.9918832757409454, \"rank\": 0.008183144587498664, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phenotype\"}, {\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klinefelter_syndrome\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3306794939520954e-46, \"text\": \"XXY\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klinefelter_syndrome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klinefelter_syndrome\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"high testosterone levels\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"the presence\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 2999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a right-wing fantasy, aided in these cases by the practice of so-called sex-testing in sports.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a right-wing fantasy\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"these cases\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"the practice\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"so-called sex-testing\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I say \\\"so called\\\" because these tests in no way actually test for something so dependent on multiple characteristics and determinations as a person's sex.\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{